src/serial/ll-dgr-src/prestream_f.f File Reference

Detailed Description

Pre-Stream and Strean steps for order parameter distribution function f in the dual grid D2Q9 Lee-Lin multiphase LBM.

The pre-stream step is done in f, which is then streamed into fbar.

Directional differentials are evaluated using a second order switching differential scheme (biased/central). Other differentials are evaluated using a standard second order central differencing scheme.
